{"tid":2153539,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★涉嫌洗錢　多間中資公司辦公室遭印度稅局搜查","createTime":"2020-08-12T14:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T14:52:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1af3c220ef9eabb11919d17982a69fd38e1c814a","tid":2153539,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"中印緊張局勢升溫之際，印度稅局近日突擊搜查多間中資公司的辦公室，涉嫌洗錢。當中一名中國籍的公司負責人，涉持有偽造的印度護照而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n印度稅局發聲明指出，有數名中國人、其合作夥伴及銀行職員，涉嫌通過空殼公司洗錢。搜查行動中發現，多間空殼實體建立逾40個銀行帳戶，期間獲得逾100億印度盧比（約10.37億港元）的信貸。行動中涉事公司的中國籍負責人羅桑（Luo Sang，音譯）被捕。<br />\n聲明指出，一家中資公司的分支機構以及有關方，通過向空殼實體收取虛假預付款的方式，取得逾10億印度盧比（約1億港元），據指是要在印度開設「零售演示廳」。此外，當局亦發現涉及港元和美元的交易證據，正進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200812/bkn-20200812144248700-0812_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200812%2Fbkn-20200812144248700-0812_00952_001.html&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7bc0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=0cb769c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200812/bkn-20200812144248700-0812_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"419850add6c835eb51e11b319a93f5c3fa588284","tid":2153539,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3078f75430401ce99281fa30157b2c392f2da1","tid":2153539,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"支國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" c